===Noun===
'''trapezoid''' (''plural:'' '''trapezoids''')

#{{geometry}} (''UK'') A [[convex]] [[quadrilateral]] with no two sides parallel (known as a [[trapezium]] in US English).
#{{geometry}} (''US'') A [[convex]] [[quadrilateral]] with two non-adjacent parallel sides (called a [[trapezium]] in British English).
#(''anatomy'') The [[trapezoid bone]] of the [[wrist]].

